{
  "stem": "1641.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "And then the sugar and the salt.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "And they all had their own barrel, which they then carted away, when it was-- everything was emptied.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "And the crockery and cutlery had to be taken.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "And they only left the bare-- they took out the light bulbs.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "And they took everything what-- what could be taken.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "So they robbed 32,000 people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "Well, I mean, there was a fair bit of material left over.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 76,
      "text": "And after a few days, then we had to go to the Dreher beer factory.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 77,
      "text": "That was a big factory, where they Gestapo had its headquarters.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 78,
      "text": "And under the Gestapo were all the Hungarian interrogators and inquisitors.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 79,
      "text": "We called them just inquisitors, because they arrested, every day, a few dozen of the leading citizens.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 80,
      "text": "They arrested the doctors, solicitors, accountants, bank managers, wholesale merchants-- impor-- anybody who-- who had a bit of wealth, or a middle-class person.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 81,
      "text": "They didn't worry about factory workers or very poor Jews, only the ones who had some assets.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But they already took their homes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They already took their-- their whole property and everything what was in their homes.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But that wasn't enough of the-- for them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They started to beat these people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they tortured them with the most cruel methods, not seen since-- since the darkest Middle Ages.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Bloody Jew, tell us, where did you hide your gold?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Where is your diamond?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Where-- where do you keep your diamonds?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Where do you keep your gold coins?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because they assumed that every single Jew has mountains of gold and diamonds.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Well, quite a few had-- had diamonds, because that was only way to save your assets.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You know, and the money, it was-- it wasn't-- there was a very strong inflation.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And so many Jews had diamonds.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
